### Passo 1 — Criar o `DesktopShell` (layout ERP com menu lateral)

**Arquivo novo:** `lib/core/presentation/desktop_shell.dart`

```dart
import 'package:flutter/material.dart';
import 'package:flutter_riverpod/flutter_riverpod.dart';
